This project is intended to be a light weight, flexible, 3D OpenGL ES scene graph for use, initially, with the Android platform. 

Current features include:
	- node based scene graph
	- open gl primitive library 
	- open gl object loading classes for Android
	- easy transformation management system
	- node types include
		> parents and groups
		> 2D and 3D shape nodes
		> translation, rotation, scale, shear
		> fxshape and fxgroup for managing more dynamic groups
		> lights
		> materials
		
Immediate project goals include:
	- implement picking system
	- camera nodes
	- effects 
	- and more... 